data.title: About Vincent
data.meta_description: Often appearing grumpy or absent-minded, I'm actually a very fun guy. If you get to know me. And I like you. Which is not necessarily the case... What with all the selfish, unfriendly people in the world... If you ask me, they should *reverts to unintelligible mumbling*
